text: The Hong Kong women's national handball team is the national team of Hong Kong. It is governed by the Handball Association of Hong Kong and takes part in international handball competitions. ==Asian Championship record== * 1989 – 5th * 2015 – 8th * 2017 – 8th * 2018 – 7th ==External links== * *IHF profile Category:Women's national handball teams Hand National team
title: Hong Kong women's national handball team
